{
  "id": 5085102657503232,
  "name": "Clipboardchange event",
  "summary": "The \"clipboardchange\" event fires whenever the system clipboard contents are changed either by a web app or any other system application. This allows web-apps like remote desktop clients to keep their clipboards synchronized with the system clipboard. It provides an efficient alternative to polling the clipboard(using Javascript) for changes.",
