  "debuggability": "To improve debuggability, developers should be able to set breakpoints directly in their code where the clipboardchange event listener is registered, using the Sources tool as with any other event. Additionally, clipboardchange will be available alongside other clipboard-related events—such as copy, cut, and paste—in the “Clipboard” section of Event Listener Breakpoints within the Sources tool.",
